touchpad-emulator (0.0-2) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add --sensitivity CLI argument to control cursor speed divisor
  * Add Xiaomi Pad 6S Pro to known devices list
  * Skip EVIOCGRAB for button devices with EV_SW events (SW_LID) so logind
    can still receive lid open/close events
  * Fix LaunchTouchpadEmulator.sh: replace echo -e with printf for portability
  * Update README with device table and CLI arguments documentation

